<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="play-n">play <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pleɪ/    美 /pleɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 玩耍；游戏；嬉戏；比赛：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>at play</strong> 
在玩耍</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Play is very important to a child’s development. 
游戏对孩子的成长十分重要。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 戏剧；剧本：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>go to a play 
去看戏</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>put on / perform a play</strong> 
演戏</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>playful /playful/ adj   </p></div>